Module uk.gov.gchq.eventlogging
Package event.logging.impl

Interface EventSerializer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEventSerializer
    public interface EventSerializer
    This interface is used to define a method that will serialise an Event object tree into a String representation of the object. The default EventSerializer implementation is DefaultEventSerializer.
